sectiondef.header: Structures and functions for parsing CRLs

detaileddescription.para: Certificate revocation list entry. Contains the CA-specific serial numbers and revocation dates.

Some fields of this structure are publicly readable. Do not modify them except via Mbed TLS library functions: the effect of modifying those fields or the data that those fields points to is unspecified.
Certificate revocation list structure. Every CRL may have multiple entries.

briefdescription.para: Parse a DER-encoded CRL and append it to the chained list.

simplesect.para: If MBEDTLS_USE_PSA_CRYPTO is enabled, the PSA crypto subsystem must have been initialized by calling psa_crypto_init() before calling this function.

parameterdescription.para: points to the start of the chain
buffer holding the CRL data in DER format
size of the buffer (including the terminating null byte for PEM data)

simplesect.para: 0 if successful, or a specific X509 or PEM error code

briefdescription.para: Parse one or more CRLs and append them to the chained list.

simplesect.para: Multiple CRLs are accepted only if using PEM format
If MBEDTLS_USE_PSA_CRYPTO is enabled, the PSA crypto subsystem must have been initialized by calling psa_crypto_init() before calling this function.

parameterdescription.para: points to the start of the chain
buffer holding the CRL data in PEM or DER format
size of the buffer (including the terminating null byte for PEM data)

simplesect.para: 0 if successful, or a specific X509 or PEM error code

briefdescription.para: Load one or more CRLs and append them to the chained list.

simplesect.para: Multiple CRLs are accepted only if using PEM format
If MBEDTLS_USE_PSA_CRYPTO is enabled, the PSA crypto subsystem must have been initialized by calling psa_crypto_init() before calling this function.

parameterdescription.para: points to the start of the chain
filename to read the CRLs from (in PEM or DER encoding)

simplesect.para: 0 if successful, or a specific X509 or PEM error code

memberdef.argsstring: (char *buf, size_t size, const char *prefix, const mbedtls_x509_crl *crl)
memberdef.name: mbedtls_x509_crl_info

briefdescription.para: Returns an informational string about the CRL.

simplesect.para: The length of the string written (not including the terminated nul byte), or a negative error code.
